doing today, Martinez?</i>

14
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,689
Making sure the MAV
is still upright?

15
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,807
<i>MARTINEZ: I'd like you to know</i>

16
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:35,927
<i>that visual inspection
of the equipment...</i>

17
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,604
