FEMALE <i>AUTOMATED</i> VOICE:
<i>Warning. Suit breach detected.</i>

98
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,727
What happened?

99
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,801
He was hit.

100
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,961
Watney, report.

101
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,761
Before we lost telemetry,

102
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:54,887
