103
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,087
LEWIS: Where did you
last see him?

104
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,241
I don't know where he is.

105
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,321
LEWIS: What are the vitals
on his suit?

106
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,401
